{"tid":2009592,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【王家衛好拍檔】香港導演羅文病逝，終年70歲","createTime":"2020-05-10T00:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:08:01.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a597143e4a9dca52fb4a8bbf233e58ccf122e652","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:19:03.000Z","msg":"【王家衛好拍檔】導演羅文病逝 終年70歲<br />\n香港時間05月09日(六)<br />\n15:59更新 15:17建立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200509163802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200509163802&h=dae087d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演羅文病逝，終年70歲。<br />\n<br />\n導演羅文昨日心臟衰竭病逝，終年70歲。羅導於1966年加入邵氏兄弟電影公司，先任化妝師，後因認識了吳思遠而「轉戰」影壇，先後與吳思遠攜手合作電影《退休探長》與《阿燦當差》等，二人認識超過數十年，可謂私交甚篤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200509163802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200509163802&h=82fe2eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演羅文於1966年已入行任化妝師。<br />\n<br />\n對於好友離世，吳思遠受訪說：「佢係我加入邵氏認識嘅第一個人，一直都有保持聯絡，近年佢都出出入入醫院好多次。（後事處理中？）等佢家人通知，我就幫手話畀啲朋友知，總之幫得就幫啦。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，羅文加入影圈後試過與已故編劇黃炳耀組電影公司，1990年開始為多部電影擔任監制及策劃等工作，曾有份為王家衛執導的《東邪西毒》、《東成西就》、《重慶森林》等出力。而羅文最後執導的電影為關之琳主演的《1/2次同床》。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，王家衛上月曾到醫院探望羅文，當時羅文仍精神奕奕，後來更加出院返家休息，故當接獲對方突然離世消息，王家衛感到驚愕兼婉惜，希望其家人節哀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/bkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fbkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001.html&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=40716fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/bkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e6d1e9f9872417ba6de8f11c6de843d00e6e920","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:20:18.000Z","msg":"【一路好走】導演羅文病逝 王家衛悼念故友 (21:49)<br />\n文章日期：2020年05月09日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200509/s00009/c059c6b29bc9db60cff0878ca9f4f8fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200509%2Fs00009%2Fc059c6b29bc9db60cff0878ca9f4f8fa.jpg&h=157c2477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演羅文（左一）與王家衛（左二）是多年好友，合作無間。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n曾執導電影《阿燦當差》、《獵鷹計劃》與《人魚傳說》的導演羅文昨日因心臟衰竭病逝，終年70歲。羅文跟王家衛是多年老友，曾在澤東擔任製片與幕後工作。王家衛對好友病逝感惋惜，他回覆《明報》稱上月曾到醫院探望羅文，知道他的病况有好轉曾出院。昨日接到羅文離世的消息感到好突然，願一路好走。<br />\n<br />\n導演羅文於1960年代加入邵氏，早期擔任化妝師工作。後來認識了吳思遠，成為好友，羅文並參與電影製作。1980年代執導多部電影，合作演員包括周潤發、王祖賢、劉德華、鍾楚紅等。最後執導電影1996年的《1/2次同床》劉德華與關之琳主演。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200509/1589031460154/【一路好走】導演羅文病逝-王家衛悼念故友\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200509%2F1589031460154%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E5%A5%BD%E8%B5%B0%E3%80%91%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E7%BE%85%E6%96%87%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%9B%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E6%95%85%E5%8F%8B&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=76bdbddf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200509%2F1589031460154%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E5%A5%BD%E8%B5%B0%E3%80%91%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E7%BE%85%E6%96%87%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%9B%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E6%95%85%E5%8F%8B&h=42ae9f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200509/1589031460154/【一路好走】導演羅文病逝-王家衛悼念故友</a>"},{"pid":"b4eb607508f1b249ed1fe414426fd50ef06ff2da","tid":2009592,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"好可惜 佢唱歌咬字超清"},{"pid":"f9668f0918e71e069ad107cb81df6eec6fdb105f","tid":2009592,"uid":81312,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"又要見到班偽人喊苦喊忽"},{"pid":"60b27975ddd49e129140cfdb410835a14820887e","tid":2009592,"uid":239842,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4eb607508f1b249ed1fe414426fd50ef06ff2da","tid":2009592,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"好可惜 佢唱歌咬字超清"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:59:16.000Z","msg":"唱歌個羅文死左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a47d45e2091f32865da276eee3dc6a2e686399","tid":2009592,"uid":62192,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:01:29.000Z","msg":"羅文又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d33d4af7a534eadd8f2601dcbf5d149335bb1ff","tid":2009592,"uid":3776,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"難得一生好本領"},{"pid":"80b8cf91561295c1202ae982c58073dc8802c4ea","tid":2009592,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"羅記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408d06db9ca6c086cee583fe5798f2ba594a1c2a","tid":2009592,"uid":271545,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:34:55.000Z","msg":"佢上次死我喊左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f7a9d38fdc3cf12c94cdc14d19be0fb2036b09","tid":2009592,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"我地大家 在獅子山下相遇上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac