ps://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/bkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fbkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001.html&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=40716fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/bkn-20200509151725167-0509_00862_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"f180f4643e9696df0728e2e1a1c1da230b87a944","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7711701cf8480f0938cf75678c5920b8540804db","tid":2009592,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"張衛健嗰套「倫文敍老點柳先開」個導演<br />\n套戲幾搞笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"係阿王好少有嘅笑片"},{"pid":"6b78c42a95b538caf0e26460df1b49a7b6445c90","tid":2009592,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a47d45e2091f32865da276eee3dc6a2e686399","tid":2009592,"uid":62192,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:01:29.000Z","msg":"羅文又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"孟德拉效應"},{"pid":"6bd2e1bebfdba93e82cfb269c324684efd52be5b","tid":2009592,"uid":37396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"點解光加熱係等於火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9cf7423034b73130633c1d393a23e9857bf8c2","tid":2009592,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f180f4643e9696df0728e2e1a1c1da230b87a944","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7711701cf8480f0938cf75678c5920b8540804db","tid":2009592,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"張衛健嗰套「倫文敍老點柳先開」個導演<br />\n套戲幾搞笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"係阿王好少有嘅笑片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"可惜配咗音"},{"pid":"828dc1b96f1dd5a62064ffd3738b7c46f3e340f5","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2d9cf7423034b73130633c1d393a23e9857bf8c2","tid":2009592,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f180f4643e9696df0728e2e1a1c1da230b87a944","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7711701cf8480f0938cf75678c5920b8540804db","tid":2009592,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"張衛健嗰套「倫文敍老點柳先開」個導演<br />\n套戲幾搞笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"係阿王好少有嘅笑片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"可惜配咗音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:03:11.000Z","msg":"因為要就埋配普通話音"},{"pid":"8d796728d8835ad4e3768676a2862dd9a99d42d1","tid":2009592,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"未睇過佢拍的戲<br />\n好慘無人識"},{"pid":"e3348a2f02e256b0791d6f700a418bc924dab40a","tid":2009592,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"家英哥難忘羅文用詠春打高球<br />\n2020年06月09日 04:15<br />\n<br />\n家英哥與導演羅文因為打高爾夫球而成為好友。<br />\n<br />\n  (星島日報報道)導演羅文（原名：羅興文）上月因心臟衰竭病逝，終年70歲。昨日於灣仔循道衛理聯合教會，以基督教儀式舉行安息禮拜。一眾圈中好友羅家英、鄭則士夫婦、張同祖、董瑋、吳思遠及蕭榮等到場送別羅文導演。<br />\n<br />\n  羅家英表示跟吳思遠、劉偉強、張同祖等8位圈中好友為羅文導演扶靈，本身跟羅文相識十幾廿年的他，指跟對方因打高球結緣：「他打波好叻，仲係詠春高手，用詠春打波㗎！我試過打波時打腫他的嘴，惟有錫番他囉！他撩我賭錢，5蚊一個洞，跟住他認真打啦！」家英哥表示去年自己因前列腺手術入院，當時羅文導演帶了兩個木瓜探望他，今年有找過對方，但未有回覆，後來在化妝師的社交網站得知對方去世消息。<br />\n<br />\n  張同祖表示跟導演羅文在邵氏年代認識，經已相識40年以上，對方說話多、風趣，而且為人很好，又指今年4月見過面，原本打算疫情穩定後探望對方，豈料已去世：「他年頭開始心臟衰竭，以前曾經做過通波仔手術。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4297460/2020-06-09/post-家英哥難忘羅文用詠春打高球/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4297460%2F2020-06-09%2Fpost-%E5%AE%B6%E8%8B%B1%E5%93%A5%E9%9B%A3%E5%BF%98%E7%BE%85%E6%96%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%A0%E6%98%A5%E6%89%93%E9%AB%98%E7%90%83%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=3ee80f9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4297460/2020-06-09/post-家英哥難忘羅文用詠春打高球/</a>"}]}